author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Concrete curb installation tips…I need to build a concrete curb for my shower backer board and bathroom drywall. But the form has a gap between it and the floor. So I used Great Stuff Big Gap Filler. Lightly spraying with water speeds up the cure. It worked perfectly to retain the new concrete.
